text: Jack Pancott (born 1 April 1933) is a British gymnast. He competed at the 1960 Summer Olympics and the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1933 births Category:Living people Category:British male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Great Britain Category:Gymnasts at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:People from Farnborough, Hampshire
